Who was featured in today's segment about bullying? How does his mother describe his behavior before the documentary was filmed? According to his mother, why and how has he changed? Why do you think that bullying occurs? How do you think it might affect both the bullies and the victims? What do you think could be done to counter the causes and effects of bullying? Explain.

